data.description:
This exceptional 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom offers a blend of comfort and style with 2,464 square feet of well-designed living space. Step inside and you'll immediately be captivated by the tall ceilings, fresh paint and large picture windows that create a bright and airy atmosphere throughout. The open living space flows seamlessly, making it idea for gatherings or entertaining friends. The heart of the home is the beautiful kitchen, a culinary enthusiast's delight, featuring ample cabinet space and a center island that invites culinary creativity. The split floorplan ensures privacy and convenience, with the master suite tucked away from the other bedrooms. Your oasis awaits with an en-suite bathroom, complete with a soaking tub, separate shower, and spacious walk-in closet. The additional three bedrooms are generously sized and ready to adapt to your needs. But the true highlight of this property is the outdoor living space! Step outside and discover a paradise of relaxation and entertainment. The crystal-clear pool invites you to cool off on hot summer days, while the soothing sound of the backyard waterfall provides a tranquil ambiance. Don't forget the convenience of a 3-car garage, offering ample storage and parking space. With this home, you'll have room for everything you need. Owner Agent.
***Photos coming 11/22***
